Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无论到哪里 都要在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:30.35,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}M.I.N.A.M.I.K.E Let's Go！
