Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(300,380)\frz19}压\N岁\N钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(720,230)\frz19}压\N岁\N钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆贺新年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年会鼓动起干劲加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点进行表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我拿起这把伞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用它把二宫同学转起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将被转起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田要几个年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了新年参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了风筝转了陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可内田还是依然每天来我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的年糕汤你吃了两块年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个一组是常识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二贯寿司放一碟也是同样的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回转寿司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  你知道贯这个单位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田在别人家里吃了一堆年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田把红豆汤都喝得一干二净了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是夏天拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这个是夏天时内田的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在会变成怎么样的惨状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太夸张了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那明天去温水泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果年末年初没有过着慵懒的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会有问题的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来泳池  到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈突然要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈总是很突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  趁这个机会为了夏天来练习游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  来帮我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  夏奈  放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  这个肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年糕太好吃的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经当不了新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到泳池却没什么可以做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是为了这个才来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想弄个特训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让内田那不像样的肚子瘦下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  特训
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  内田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那肚子是何等不堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  又不是那么严重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须趁现在缩回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  要采取地狱温水减肥特训
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像有了干劲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然接受过游泳的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还没有特训过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想特训别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就叫我魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫你魔鬼教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的泳池教学中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怨你的一不留神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来特训啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是复仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披着特训皮的复仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭之后再特训怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这里的食堂做出来的东西似乎很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的冰淇淋是最棒的享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  去吃午饭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧春香的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下回把圭子她们也叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为什么没有叫她们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是去旅行就是回老家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天一夜的南家旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肚子才是最需要特训的啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是千秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么既然肚子也饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼教官  先睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼教官尽情享受慵懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-90,0:00:-9.-90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-90,0:00:-9.-90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别大哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得比想像中的小一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是特别的漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边两个人在寒假的时候去海外旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像去看了什么有名的建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子寒假的时候去了哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去了奶奶家那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶家似乎很远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都相当远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  夏奈  特别大的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个建筑叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪你究竟去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子呢  去了哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？喂  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考虑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  三学期开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就是马拉松大会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到这个就郁闷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  马拉松大会要跑多远来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是6英里左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:57.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1英里＝1.6千米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  我以为是26英里左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说英里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过趁现在开始训练就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看春天还有体检
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始减肥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假的时候重了4磅左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:12.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1磅约＝453.6克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不注意的话就会超过100磅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说为什么是磅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说千米千克之类的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是维持着海外心情可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是海外心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海外组的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子的京都心情还没有散去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子和往常一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马拉松和体检真是郁闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被传染了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了  事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我藤冈  大家都去京都了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉松是要跑多少公里来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是10公里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我还以为是42.195公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是全长马拉松啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两步调好一致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  跑马拉松又能让人瘦多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每日坚持就不会瘦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跑10公里体重就能减2公斤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说马拉松大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  因为就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈同学的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  藤冈同学你是不是有点晒黑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假时有去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？能看的出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前被带着去单板滑雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点被雪反射的太阳光晒黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒痕像胡子一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很会滑雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦  也就还行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家都从京都回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是回来了  刚才有一瞬间变回了正常的腔调
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈说话好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-90,0:00:-9.-90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家斗恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.00,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}终于要对决了！！魔王篇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家斗恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.98,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}危险！勇者篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-85,0:00:-9.-85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是火锅好啊  吃火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为冷就提议吃火锅也太不动脑子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯那就吃火锅吧  做起来还方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要吃火锅啊  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大冷天吃火锅最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  春香  一起去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下大雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你们不知道积雪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为知道才在被炉里懒洋洋的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先从被炉里出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  别看我这样  我也是很怕冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从被炉爬出来是需要事先做心理准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香在写什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  夏奈  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出门的话就拜托你顺便买点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来春香是肯定不打算出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  我还是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  被炉取暖什么的  忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拜托千秋去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多积雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  干嘛攒雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有雪  那当然是先打雪仗再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是骨子里就喜欢胡闹的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是要大家一起决定玩什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看它这样  它是个饭团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃  扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你们是要打雪仗吗  打雪仗对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  那就来战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你们都收拾掉  战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  是很有力气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  也看棒球比赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是垒球的扔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  也是喜欢足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真下手了啊  看我这次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哦  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次投犯规球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学生对中学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  只有我是中学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一球！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有我是这幅惨状啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是小学生对中学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不公平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且别看我这样  其实都还没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快认输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香也是来打雪仗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘带钱包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他要买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(540,300)\frz-27}鬼\N面\N具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(800,360)\frz-27}节\N分\N的\N豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都走到这了  干嘛不自己去买
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  我还是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要回被炉里去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原句是节分撒豆子时说的「鬼は外」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-85,0:00:-9.-85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-85,0:00:-9.-85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节分？节分是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍不知道什么是节分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  节分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的来说  就是在家里撒豆子把恶鬼给赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把福请进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的万圣节也是  最近节日都好高雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节分从很久以前就有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来扮演鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一边说「鬼快出去」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边把这些豆撒在鬼身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去  鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要打败我的话  就准备一亿颗豆子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常人家里怎么可能有一亿颗豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是豆子也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢熊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福快来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿一亿颗出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是说了撒豆子要适度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾干净之后来吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼也在收拾豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家特制  惠方蛋糕卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节分真是个好东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一块不够  再来一块！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说鬼可以随便撒娇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是鬼嘛  撒娇有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  面具借我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再给我一块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋也再来一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鬼也能拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那我去准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  你打算在家里待到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼是要出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说  身为鬼的我要被赶走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…能帮忙的鬼留下来倒也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那鬼  帮我续一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  帮我揉揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会使唤鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  不想喝咖啡了帮我买瓶果汁回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是鬼吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干了！待遇太差干不下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  鬼要是被小看了就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来告诉你什么是真正的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  果汁还没买来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去买吧  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮我揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己揉去  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去打扫浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天轮到你打扫吧  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是平时的千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去给春香姐姐帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那只是平时的千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  千秋  这个拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要放胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.-85,0:00:-9.-85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
